# Arleen Umbay

## Executive Assistant Center Operations & Administration

Phone: **512-471-2763** |
Email: **[arleen@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:arleen@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Arleen joined TACC in 2013 and currently assists the Executive Director. Previously, she assisted an Associate Professor of Pathology at the Sylvester Comprehensive Cancer Center, University of Miami (Florida). She also worked in quality assurance at the Drug Delivery Division of Ortho McNeil Pharmaceuticals in Redwood City, California.

### Education

**B.A., Marine Biology,**  

University of California, Santa Cruz